Package: document
Title:  Document a Single R Code File
Version: 0.8.0
Authors@R: person(given = c("Andreas", "Dominik"), family = "Cullmann",
    email = "adc-r@arcor.de", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Extract roxygen2-style comments from a single R code file and 
    convert them to pdf and txt files and a temporary help page to be called 
    from within R.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
